*Initial Question & Results*


*There is currently a proposal to reduce the amount of carbon pollution
released into our air by putting a carbon pollution tax on companies that
extract or import fossil fuels like oil, coal and natural gas. The money
raised would be used provide a refund check for fifteen hundred dollars a
year per family to offset higher energy costs. *
Support vs. Oppose:

National: 58-35

Battleground: 59-33

Iowa Caucus Goers: 75-17

*After arguments on both sides*

National: 46-45

Battleground: 46-43

Iowa Caucus Goers: 68-23

